3. Which region holds the largest market share in the turbine casing market?
Currently, North America holds the largest market share in the turbine casing market, followed by Asia Pacific and Europe.

4. What are the different materials used in turbine casing manufacturing?
The materials commonly used in turbine casing manufacturing include stainless steel, carbon steel, and nickel-based alloys.

